# ReelFlow - Variáveis de Ambiente

## Supabase (Obrigatório)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key

## URLs
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

## APIs Gratuitas (Escolha pelo menos uma)
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=AIzaxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

## APIs Premium (Opcional - ativam modo Premium)
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
FLUX_API_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
SHOTSTACK_API_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

## Meta Graph API (Opcional - para postar no Instagram)
META_GRAPH_API_VERSION=v22.0
META_GRAPH_BASE_URL=https://graph.facebook.com